java.lang.Object
com.salesmanager.core.model.system.IntegrationConfiguration
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.json.simple.JSONAware
public class IntegrationConfiguration extends Object implements org.json.simple.JSONAware
Object used to contain the integration information with an external gateway Uses simple JSON to encode the object in JSON by implementing JSONAware and uses jackson JSON decode to parse JSON String to an Object
